級毒品海洛因壹包（驗餘淨重零點陸壹公克）沒收銷燬之。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TPHM/109%2c%e4%b8%8a%e8%a8%b4%2c1784%2c20200730%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TPHM,109,上訴,1784,20200730,1","JYEAR":"109","JCASE":"上訴","JNO":"1784","JDATE":"20200730","JTITLE":"毒品危害防制條例"}